                     <interp inst="t18460105-459-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>for stealing 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18460105-name-678" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18460105-name-678" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
