                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable V</hi> 95.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction at Kingston-on-Thames—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 23<hi rend="italic">rd March</hi>, 1845, and <hi rend="italic">confined six months</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
